{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"615","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"印尼擬修勞動法鬆綁解僱規定 工會號召大規模抗議","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2020-01-09 23:57&nbsp; </span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>中央社 雅加達<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>日綜合外電報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>印尼總統佐科威的政府即將在下週將勞動法修正案送交國會，準備鬆綁限制重重的印尼解僱規則。印尼工會聯盟今天揚言將動員成千上萬人走上街頭抗議，盼阻止法案過關。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>修改<span lang='EN-US'>2003</span>年的勞動法雖在印尼不受歡迎，卻是外國投資人希望佐科威（<span lang='EN-US'>Joko Widodo</span>）在第<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>任期能優先處理的事務。由於現有印尼勞動法規定的遣散費在全球數一數二豐厚，因此許多投資人認為，這影響到企業在東南亞最大經濟體印尼僱用正職員工和做出投資決定。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>佐科威的執政聯盟儘管在國會掌握<span lang='EN-US'>74%</span>席次的優勢，但若出現大規模抗議，仍可能令國會對這份具政治敏感性的法案陷入激烈辯論。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>印尼勞工聯盟（<span lang='EN-US'>Indonesian Confederation ofWorkers</span>）副主席朱米西（<span lang='EN-US'>Jumisi</span>）今天在記者會上表示，<span lang='EN-US'>13</span>日國會開議當天，超過<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>個工會的成千上萬名會員將齊聚國會大廈前抗議。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>他說：「這份法案將把我們推向貧窮深淵邊緣，我們的子子孫孫都將受到影響。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>根據印尼工會聯盟發表的聲明，佐科威政府的修法是「可悲的法案」，是「現代剝削」，將造成勞工遣散費被大砍，大量人力轉入外包，使得勞工應享有的基本權利保障消失。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>:https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4278448</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-01-10","clk_count":"16"}},"__N_SSG":true}